	<p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><i><b>Pollock</b></i> is a 2000 <a class="external" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Biographical_film" title="Biographical film">biographical</a> <a class="external" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Drama_film" title="Drama film">drama film</a> which tells the life story of painter <a class="external" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jackson_Pollock" title="Jackson Pollock">Jackson Pollock</a>. It stars <a class="external" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ed_Harris" title="Ed Harris">Ed Harris</a>, <a class="external" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jennifer_Connelly" title="Jennifer Connelly">Jennifer Connelly</a>, <a class="external" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Robert_Knott&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" title="Robert Knott (page does not exist)">Robert Knott</a>, <a class="external" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bud_Cort" title="Bud Cort">Bud Cort</a>, <a class="external" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Molly_Regan&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" title="Molly Regan (page does not exist)">Molly Regan</a>, <a class="external" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Marcia_Gay_Harden" title="Marcia Gay Harden">Marcia Gay Harden</a> and <a class="external" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sada_Thompson" title="Sada Thompson">Sada Thompson</a>.</p>
	<h2 xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"> <span class="mw-headline" id="Cast">Cast</span></h2>
	<ul xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
	  <li><a class="external" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ed_Harris" title="Ed Harris">Ed Harris</a> as <a class="external" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jackson_Pollock" title="Jackson Pollock">Jackson Pollock</a></li>
