	<h2 xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"> <span class="mw-headline" id="Soundtrack">Soundtrack</span></h2>
	<p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">The film was released on <a class="external" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/CD" title="CD">CD</a> on February 13, 2001. <a class="external" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jeff_Beal" title="Jeff Beal">Jeff Beal</a> is the composer for the film.</p>
